 2014-12532014-11-06,  TC,  FIN,  ,  , 
ActCanada Marine Act
SubjectQuebec Port Authority Borrowing Limit ** Increase **
PrecisOrder approving the Supplementary Letters Patent provisions amending Article 9 of the Letters Patent issued to the Quebec Port Authority to increase from $46,000,000 to $110,000,000 the aggregate limit on the borrowings which the Quebec Port Authority is empowered to make on the credit of the Port Authority for port purposes.
